OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDo more to spur investment,
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffirms urge government      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The CBI group is calling for a         
OL,6, permanent "super-deduction" tax break  
OL,7, to boost business investment in the UK.
OL,9,FThe super-deduction allowance currently
OL,10,Fgives businesses investing in certain  
OL,11,Ftypes of equipment, like machinery, a  
OL,12,Fmuch higher tax reduction than usual.  
OL,14,FIt was introduced at the spring Budget 
OL,15,Flast year, but is due to expire in     
OL,16,FMarch 2023.                            
OL,18,F"It's started the job but cannot be a  
OL,19,Fone-hit wonder," CBI director general  
OL,20,FTony Danker said.                      
